<view class="c13-drawer-page c13-step-three">
  <view class="c13-bg-report">
    <view class="c13-status"><text>9:41</text><text>wifi</text></view>
    <view class="c13-bg-top">
      <button bindtap="onRefreshExercise">‹</button>
      <text>完整报告</text>
      <text>错题 1 / 8</text>
    </view>
    <text class="c13-bg-title">AI 提分报告（完整）</text>
    <text class="c13-bg-time">报告生成时间：2024-05-30 10:36</text>
    <image class="c13-bg-owl c13-pointer-owl" src="/assets/clean-icons/owl-teacher-pointer-clean.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <view class="c13-bg-score full">
      <view class="c13-score-row">
        <image class="c13-score-icon" src="/assets/clean-icons/shield-check-purple.png" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view><text>可追回分数</text><text class="c13-score-sub">可优先改善</text></view>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-score-value"><text>6-10</text><text>分</text><text>↑</text></view>
      <text class="c13-score-note">通过优先修复关键错因，有机会追回的分数区间</text>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="c13-overlay dark"></view>

  <view class="c13-drawer">
    <view class="c13-handle"></view>
    <view class="c13-drawer-head">
      <text>修复这道关键错题</text>
      <button bindtap="onRefreshExercise">×</button>
    </view>
    <view class="c13-progress">
      <view class="c13-line active-three"></view>
      <view class="c13-step done"><text>1</text><text>错因诊断</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step done"><text>2</text><text>换法讲解</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step active"><text>3</text><text>验证练习</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step"><text>4</text><text>掌握判断</text></view>
    </view>
    <scroll-view class="c13-drawer-scroll" scroll-y="true" enhanced="true" show-scrollbar="false">
      <view class="c13-panel exercise-panel">
        <view class="c13-practice-head">
          <text>做 1 道同类验证题</text>
          <text>只做 1 道即时验证题</text>
        </view>
        <text class="c13-question">甲、乙两车同时从 A 地出发，甲每小时行 70km，乙每小时行 55km，3 小时后甲比乙多行多少千米？</text>
        <view class="c13-options">
          <button bindtap="onSelectOption" data-option="40 千米"><text>A</text><text>40 千米</text></button>
          <button bindtap="onSelectOption" data-option="45 千米"><text>B</text><text>45 千米</text></button>
          <button bindtap="onSelectOption" data-option="50 千米"><text>C</text><text>50 千米</text></button>
          <button bindtap="onSelectOption" data-option="55 千米"><text>D</text><text>55 千米</text></button>
        </view>
        <button class="c13-primary" bindtap="onSubmitAnswer">提交答案</button>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>
</view>
